snippet.title: Judero | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
The stop motion action commences on September the 16th! 
Discover the mythical Scottish Borders. Play as Judero, a pagan seer with the ability to possess animals, and embark on an adventure unlike any other. All hand animated in glorious stop motion!
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1960900/Judero/
